title: The Unwritten (001 - 054 + Apocalypse 01 - 05 ) (2009 - 2014) (D
description:
The Unwritten (001 - 054 + Apocalypse 01 - 05 ) (2009 - 2014) (Digital) (Empire)

Created by Mike Carey and Peter Gross (who previously had a lengthy creative partnership on Lucifer), The Unwritten follows Tom Taylor, a man whose very existence has been tied to a fictional boy wizard through the manipulations of his father.

After the conclusion of the volume with issue #54, this title was re-launched with The Unwritten, Apocalypse which continues directly on from #54
